<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 200, alt: "Tatjana Tanaskovic Profile Image", class: 'profile-image' %>
          <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilazed %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilazed %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>Hi, my name is Tatjana Tanaskovic and I'm a Software Developer and Tech-enthusiast. My favorite programming language is Ruby and it's framework Ruby on Rails. I also work with JavaScript and it's libraries React and Redux.
          </p>
          <p>I love modern technologies and computer programming and really enjoy working in that field. Besides that I very much enjoy to spend my free time in nature environment, walking or swimming, and reading a good book. 
          </p>
           <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Mentor Software Developer, Rails Girls Beograd - Belgrade, Serbia (Jun 2018 - Present)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Software Developer, Freelance - Belgrade, Serbia (Oct 2017 - Present)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Administrator, Javni Beleznik - Pancevo, Serbia (May 2017 - Oct 2017)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Administrator, Prave vrednosti Start Up - Belgrade, Serbia (Mar 2015 - Sep 2016)
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bachelor of Science (BSc) Electrical Engineer of Computer Science (GPA 8.45), School of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science Professional Studies (VISER), Belgrade, Serbia (2011 - 2013)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Graduate student of Theology (GPA 8.65), University of East Sarajevo, Faculty of Orthodox Theology, Bosnia and Herzegovina (2001 - 2008)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Computer Science Technician, Secondary School Mladenovac, Serbia (1991 - 1995)
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
  
